<H1>Creating a signature</H1>

<P>To create a signature set the variables <STRONG>sign</STRONG> and 
<STRONG>Sign</STRONG> in the <SAMP>.mailrc</SAMP> file. For example:</P>

<PRE WIDTH=80>   <STRONG>set sign='Lost in hyperspace'</STRONG>
</PRE>

<P>This creates the signature <EM>Lost in hyperspace</EM> that
the user can add to the end of their mail messages.</P>

<PRE WIDTH=80>   <STRONG>set Sign='Fax: +44 31 453 9732'</STRONG>
</PRE>

<P>This creates the signature <SAMP>Fax: +44 31 453 9732</SAMP> that
the user can add to the end of their mail messages.</P>

